name: Taylor Swift
text: I'll be streaming 2 of the songs from the Speak Now/Help Now rehearsal performance worldwide- Saturday at 9pm central on taylorswift.com :)

name: Taylor Swift
text: Standing on my new stage doing an interview for 60 Minutes next season- cannot believe this tour is about to start!!!! Eeee!!!

name: Taylor Swift
text: I decided to open up our last tour rehearsal to the public! all ticket sales will go to tornado victims. Go to taylorswift.com for tickets!

name: Taylor Swift
text: You guys got me nominated for the Billboard Fan Favorite Award!You can go to Billboard.com to, you know, vote for whoever your favorite is:)

name: Taylor Swift

name: Taylor Swift
text: The 'mean' music video premieres on CMT in a half hour here in Nashville! 10pm eastern, 9pm central!

name: Taylor Swift
text:
Excited about tonight's tv line up! Gonna watch the debut of the Mean video at 10pm on

name: Taylor Swift

name: Taylor Swift

name: Taylor Swift
text: Headed back to Nashville after the MET Ball in NYC. Wondrous, magical, fantastic gowns EVERYWHERE. I had a really wonderful time.
